  "title": "Manager, Business Planning (Japanese-speaking) – Banking Client",
  "description": "<ul><li>Well-established brand name</li><li>APAC coverage</li><li>Excellent progression opportunities</li></ul><p>A Banking client is seeking a <strong>Business Planning Manager </strong>to join the team. This is a role which will support APAC Coverage for Business Planning responsibilities, specifically within Credit Risk. You will cover end to end execution strategic planning – coordination, administration and reporting for the credit risk department. You will have face time with key stakeholders in the business, and the opportunity to be part of a bank’s planning department.</p><p>The ideal candidate should have at least 5-8 years relevant experience within banking. Japanese language is a pre-requisite for the role as your stakeholders will be with native Japanese. Strong communication skills, time management and stakeholder management skills will be a strong advantage for the role.</p><p>If you are keen, please click on the link to apply or email me with your updated CV at Rachel.ljy@ethosbc.com. Look forward to hearing back, thank you.<br /></p><p>Reg. No. R1987809<br />BeathChapman Pte Ltd<br />Licence no. 16S8112</p>",
